import { StyleSheet } from "react-native"



export const s = StyleSheet.create ({
  container: {
      backgroundColor: "#00bfa6"
  },
  container1: { backgroundImage: "none", minHeight: "816px",
    alignItems:"center"
},
  text: { 
        paddingTop: "25px",
        paddingRight: "78px",
        paddingBottom: "30px",
        paddingLeft: 0,
        alignItems:"center",
        color:"white",
        textTransform:"capitalize"
     },
  h2: {
      fontSize: "3.75rem",
      fontWeight: 700,
      marginTop: "9px",
      marginRight: "12px",
      marginBottom: 0,
      marginLeft: 0
    },
    ".u-section-1 .u-text-2": {
      letterSpacing: "normal",
      textTransform: "none",
      fontWeight: 400,
      longForm: "none solid rgb(128, 128, 128)",
      marginTop: "12px",
      marginRight: "12px",
      marginBottom: 0,
      marginLeft: 0
    },
  form: { height: "443px",      marginTop: "20px",
    marginRight: "24px",
    marginBottom: 0,
    marginLeft: 0,
    flex:1,
    alignItems:"center"
   },
    label: { 
      width: "89px",
      marginTop: "30px",
      flex:1,
      alignItems:"center"
     },
    input: { 
      padding: "1rem",
      backgroundColor: "white",
      color: "white",
      borderRadius: "2rem"
     },
    form1: { 
      marginLeft: "0",
      flex:1,
      alignItems:"center"
     },

    button: {
      backgroundImage: "none",
      borderStyle: "none",
      textTransform: "uppercase",
      fontSize: "1.25rem",
      letterSpacing: "3px",
      width: "55%",
      paddingTop: "19px",
      paddingRight: "30px",
      paddingBottom: "21px",
      paddingLeft: 0
    },

    container2: { 
        backgroundColor: "white",
        paddingTop: "8px",
        paddingRight: "0px",
        paddingBottom: "8px",
        paddingLeft: 0
     },
    image: {
      width: "190px",
      height: "189px",
      backgroundImage: 'url("images/fd.jpg")',
      backgroundPosition: "center",
      marginTop: "20px",
      marginRight: "auto",
      marginBottom: 0,
      marginLeft: "48px",
      borderRadius: "50%"
    },
    h4: {
      fontWeight: 700,
      letterSpacing: "1px",
      fontSize: "1.875rem",
      marginTop: "-149px",
      marginRight: "63px",
      marginBottom: 0,
      marginLeft: "326px"
    },
    h5: {
      letterSpacing: "1px",
      fontSize: "1.125rem",
      fontWeight: 500,
      marginTop: "32px",
      marginRight: "95px",
      marginBottom: 0,
      marginLeft: "326px"
    },
    text2: {
      fontSize: "1.375rem",
      marginTop: "92px",
      marginRight: "84px",
      marginBottom: 0,
      marginLeft: "76px"
    },
    containerTable: { width: "564px",       marginTop: "50px",
    marginRight: "auto",
    marginBottom: 0,
    marginLeft: "auto" },
    table: { minHeight: "100px" },
    tableBody: {
      backgroundImage: "none",
      fontSize: "1.5rem",
      fontWeight: 400
    },
    td: {
      textAlign: "center",
    }
  })
